Takuma Watanabe <takumaw@sfo.kuramae.ne.jp>
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr path_helper 8
.Sh BUGS
Currently, Proxy Auto-Configuration (PAC) scripts are not supported.
You have to manually specify your proxy servers in the System Preferences.